RECORDING

### empty slot -> click rec
! recordingQue ! true
! recordingQue ! false
! content ! true
! recording ! true

### recording clip -> click to play
! playingQue ! true
! playingQue ! false
! recording ! false
! playing ! true

### recording clip -> delete clip
! content ! false
! recording ! false

### recording clip -> click to stop clip
! playing ! false

PLAYING
### stopped clip -> click to play
! playingQue ! true
! playingQue ! false
! playing ! true

### play clip -> click to stop clip
! playing ! false

